Documentation notes

--To change the global logo: file skin/theme_resources/stylesheets/images/logo_wide.png
--Featured portlet, on the top, right side: 
Any News Item can appear there, as long as it is categorized as 'featured-top' and it's state is 'Featured'
The title appears first, then the image, and on hover the summary of the News Item.
-- You can customize the right column and footer by adding/removing portlets by clicking their "Manage portlets" links
